#
# Template:
# Change a quadratic function from standard form to vertex form,
# and the find the function's domain and range.
# No fractions are involved.
#
#       f(x) = -x^2 + ax + b
#
# a is even.
#
# Last updated: Carl Yao, 1/11/2016
# ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBCCSS('A-REI.4.b')
